1474
00:52:17,580 --> 00:52:19,980
but it's Lagrange's equations of motion.

1475
00:52:21,600 --> 00:52:23,820
This is the expression for an energy.

1476
00:52:24,360 --> 00:52:25,420
Let's suppose

1477
00:52:26,120 --> 00:52:30,980
that the field did not vary with position in space.

1478
00:52:31,220 --> 00:52:32,520
Just to make the story simple,

1479
00:52:32,760 --> 00:52:37,100
let's ignore the gradients of the field

1480
00:52:37,100 --> 00:52:38,760
