00:54:19,620 --> 00:54:20,560
Do you remember how to work out

1527
00:54:20,560 --> 00:54:22,260
the equation of motion for Lagrangian?

1528
00:54:24,740 --> 00:54:27,440
You take partial of L with respect to phi dot.

1529
00:54:29,180 --> 00:54:34,080
That's A of T cubed times phi dot.

1530
00:54:34,760 --> 00:54:36,860
And then take the time derivative of that.

1531
00:54:37,880 --> 00:54:39,140
That's the left-hand side.

1532
00:54:40,380 --> 00:54:41,880
What about the right-hand side?

