00:54:46,200 --> 00:54:47,000
Anybody remember?

1534
00:54:49,840 --> 00:54:50,760
Dv d phi.

1535
00:54:52,040 --> 00:54:52,920
Like a force.

1536
00:54:52,920 --> 00:54:53,820
Like dv dx.

1537
00:54:54,840 --> 00:54:55,900
Like dv dx,

1538
00:54:55,900 --> 00:54:57,180
except there's the A cubed here.

1539
00:54:58,360 --> 00:55:02,920
A cubed dv or dv d phi.

1540
00:55:04,020 --> 00:55:05,680
dv d phi is the slope.

1541
00:55:06,060 --> 00:55:07,520
And it's the force term

1542
00:55:08,180 --> 00:55:11,180
which creates what would be an ordinary acceleration

1543
