But A is not constant with time,

1545
00:55:16,240 --> 00:55:17,780
so we have a little bit of work to do

1546
00:55:18,920 --> 00:55:20,380
to take this derivative.

1547
00:55:21,020 --> 00:55:22,340
To take the derivative,

1548
00:55:22,340 --> 00:55:23,680
what is the derivative?

1549
00:55:23,960 --> 00:55:24,060
Well,

1550
00:55:24,060 --> 00:55:24,920
the first term,

1551
00:55:24,980 --> 00:55:27,220
the d by dt acts on the phi dot.

1552
00:55:27,460 --> 00:55:32,820
And that gives us A cubed times phi double dot,

1553
00:55:34,080 --> 00:55:35,840
which is like the acceleration.

1554
00:55:36,080 --> 00:55:38,480
Not the acceleration of the expansion of the universe,

