00:56:06,160 --> 00:56:08,250
But I want to divide both

1564
00:56:08,250 --> 00:56:10,340
sides of the equation by A cubed,

1565
00:56:10,520 --> 00:56:11,730
just to get rid of as

1566
00:56:11,730 --> 00:56:12,940
many A cubed as I can.

1567
00:56:14,020 --> 00:56:14,720
All right?

1568
00:56:15,020 --> 00:56:16,440
So on the right-hand side,

1569
00:56:16,540 --> 00:56:17,820
I'll just have dv d phi.

1570
00:56:22,300 --> 00:56:23,720
And on the left-hand side,

1571
00:56:23,840 --> 00:56:24,920
I'll get rid of this A cubed.

1572
00:56:26,060 --> 00:56:28,300
I'll get rid of A squared,

1573
00:56:29,220 --> 00:56:31,360
but it will leave me with

1574
00:56:31,360 --> 00:56:33,500
a 1 over A in the denominator.

1575
00:56:34,860 --> 00:56:36,740
So let's put 1 over A,

1576
