There's another name for it.

1579
00:56:45,780 --> 00:56:46,760
Not the square root of H.

1580
00:56:46,840 --> 00:56:48,780
Not the square root of H.

1581
00:56:48,900 --> 00:56:49,100
It's H.

1582
00:56:50,780 --> 00:56:51,260
Right.

1583
00:56:52,300 --> 00:56:53,080
Just H.

1584
00:56:53,660 --> 00:56:55,440
So this is the Hubble constant.

1585
00:56:58,300 --> 00:56:58,780
Now,

1586
00:56:58,780 --> 00:56:59,820
have you ever seen...

1587
00:56:59,820 --> 00:56:59,920
Oh,

