00:56:59,920 --> 00:57:00,580
this is minus.

1589
00:57:00,780 --> 00:57:01,820
There should be a minus here.

1590
00:57:01,960 --> 00:57:03,040
Minus dv d phi.

1591
00:57:04,840 --> 00:57:05,320
Yeah,

1592
00:57:05,320 --> 00:57:06,340
minus dv d phi.

1593
00:57:07,640 --> 00:57:09,430
Force is proportional to minus

1594
00:57:09,430 --> 00:57:11,220
